y publicists who feel obliged to put something on the record, but donotwant to capture public attention-the time to \\\"bury\\\" a news story.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"publicists\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"public attention\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"a news story\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A reasonably strong statement, at that point, might have been categorized as \\\"too little, too late.\\\"\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A reasonably strong statement\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this was not a strong statement.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a strong statement\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Holy See was saddened\\\" is began.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Holy See\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saddened?\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Are we only \\\"saddened\\\" by public mockery of someone we love?\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public mockery\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact the Vatican (deliberately?)\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"missed the essential point.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the essential point\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The statement went on to \\\"deplore the offense caused to many Christians and believers of other religions,\\\" and later referred to \\\"allusions ridiculing the religious convictions of many people.\\\"\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9940371136352384, \"rank\": 0.00569744309140708, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The statement\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"the offense\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"believers\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"other religions\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"allusions\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"the religious convictions\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The show in question had not included a few \\\"allusions\\\" that mocked religion; it was a sustained attack.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The show\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"a few \\\"allusions\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"a sustained attack\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More important, the show was not merely an offense against Christians; it was an offense against God.\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9940371136352384, \"rank\": 0.00569744309140708, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou